We completely updated the design of the application and added new functionality.

We have added the ability to backup all diary entries to the Google Drive cloud. Also from now on every day we will show inspiring quotes with beautiful pictures in the application. See the menu items Backup and Restore and Inspiration in the side menu. And write to us how you like it!

We have added new improvements! Now there is an opportunity to share gratitude with the recipient. You no longer have to think about the save button in the Gratitude Diary. The new entry is saved automatically. Improved the work of deep links and animations in the application. How to share gratitude You need to swipe the thank you note to the left and click on the Share icon. Practice being happy!

We have improved the saving of unfinished entries in the Wishes and Gratitude diaries Made a number of technical improvements What does saving an unfinished recording mean If you are typing a wish or gratitude and at this time the phone calls you then all the text you entered will be saved.

Reminders added! Reminders will help you relieve your head and not worry about forgetting to write something down. Reminder feature: the ability to enter your own text. For example: Hey Beauty! : Let s make a recording! Open the side menu of the application and look for the Reminders item

Updated design of the Emotion Diary entries screen Added a description of the Diary of Emotions which will help you understand how to correctly how often and why to record emotions Added a Statistics screen where you can clearly see in which period there are more records and in which period there are fewer Added animations to the Wishes Diary and Gratitude Diary

Added new interesting functionality Random Desires Fixed a critical bug with increasing days in the Wish Diary Random Wishes will help you choose your desire or come up with a new one! They are suitable for beginners who have just started keeping a diary and for experienced ones who have already completed more than one cycle. If you are not in the mood if you want new ideas if you want to spy on what desires you might have then you need to try Random Desires! Smooth animation and the most creative options inside. How to open Random Wishes In the Wishes Diary hold down the round plus button and the Random Wishes button will appear click and go to a new screen.
